sathi shakthi ( kannada : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ತಿ ) is a 1963 indian kannada film , directed by kanagal prabhakar shastry and produced by kanagal prabhakar shastry . the film stars rajkumar , ramkumar , k. s. ashwath and b. raghavendra rao in lead roles . the film had musical score by t. g. lingappa .